net.sf.mmm.util.metakey.api

Interface MetakeyAudioVideo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MetakeyCore, MetakeyMultimedia
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MetakeyId3v2, MetakeyMovie, MetakeyMusic

    public interface MetakeyAudioVideo
extends MetakeyMultimedia
    This interface is a collection of constants defining keys for metadata-properties of audio/video content.
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)

    • Field Detail

      • DURATION

        static final String DURATION
        The duration of the audio/video content.
        ATTENTION:
        The value of this property is of the type Long and represents the duration in milliseconds.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • BPM

        static final String BPM
        The number of Beats Per Minute in the main-part of the audio.
        ATTENTION:
        The value of this property is of the type Integer.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • KEY

        static final String KEY
        The musical key the audio starts with. The ground key is represented with the according capital letter ("A"-"G") and a half key is indicated by "b" or "#". A minor key is indicated by a lower case "m". For instance Cis-Minor is represented as "C#m".
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • GENRE

        static final String GENRE
        The genre of the audio/video content. E.g. "Blues" or "Thriller".
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • PRODUCER

        static final String PRODUCER
        The name of the producer(s) of the audio/video content.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
